reviewText: I have two year old twin girls who have seen Juno on the Babyfirst channel. They love puppet characters and music, this movie was perfect for them.
My girl loves all things Juno!  The stories are great and the songs are great too! Much better to get stuck in your head versus the other stuff that's out there.
Get it on itunes, its hd 1080p and half the price. 9 more words required.  5 more words required.  Done.
